'''''Rafiki''''' ( drama film yo muri [[Kenya]] iyoborwa na  Wanuri Kahiu<ref>Rafiki - IFcinéma <nowiki>https://ifcinema.institutfrancais.com</nowiki> › movie</ref> .  ''Rafiki'' ninkuru y'urukundo rukura hagati y'abakobwa 2 bakiri bato, Kena na Ziki, hagati y'umuryango n’igitutu cya politiki gikikije uburenganzira bwa LGBT muri Kenya<ref>Rafiki - Cineuropa</ref> . Iyi filime yagaragaye bwa mbere mpuzamahanga mu gice cya ''Un Certain Regard'' mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes 2018.<ref>'Rafiki': The First Kenyan Film To Premiere At Cannes, Banned ... <nowiki>https://www.npr.org</nowiki> › 2019/04/20 › rafiki-the-first-kenya...</ref>   niyo filime ya mbere yo muri [[Kenya]] yerekanwe muri ibyo birori<ref>RAFIKI - Festival de Cannes <nowiki>https://www.festival-cannes.com</nowiki> › films › rafiki</ref>. 

== Umugambi ==
Kena afasha se John Mwaura kuyobora iduka rito ryorohereza i [[Nairobi]] mugihe yiyamamariza amatora yaho<ref>Canned in Kenya, set for Cannes: Rafiki falls foul of Nairobi ... <nowiki>https://www.theguardian.com</nowiki> › global-development › apr</ref>. Kena abana na nyina, utari mubyukuri kuvugana na John. Kena atangira gukundana na Ziki, umukobwa wabaturanyi ufite umusatsi wamabara, nawe wabaye umukobwa wa Peter Okemi, mukeba wa John muri politike<ref>Rafiki director Wanuri Kahiu on Cannes success and Kenya ban - BBC News</ref>. Kena na Ziki bafite gahunda  nyinshi z'urukundo, kandi bahita begera cyane<ref>Rafiki – Cast & Crew on MUBI <nowiki>https://mubi.com</nowiki> › films › rafiki-2018 › cast</ref>, ariko hariho amakimbirane yo kwerekana urukundo rwabo kumugaragaro kuko abaryamana bahuje ibitsina bitemewe muri Kenya<ref>Director 'saddened' by Kenyan ban on lesbian romance Rafiki (bbc.com)</ref>.

== Kwakira ==
Kuri Metacritic film ifite amanota 68 ku 100 ishingiye kubisubizo byatanzwe nabanenga 17, byerekana "muri rusange ibitekerezo byiza"<ref>Rafiki - Rotten Tomatoes <nowiki>https://www.rottentomatoes.com</nowiki> › rafiki_2019</ref>. 

